{"tid":1634520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休唔休我唔知，但文宣求大家幫手","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:36:27.000Z","uid":92277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbbdd684fa381eab98723406513a861e9fc231b","tid":1634520,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"我明依家又有休息撚又有衝衝仔<br />\n天琦講過 教條主義唔係一樣好既野，無話邊樣係100%岩邊樣係100%錯<br />\n但有樣野好明顯既係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣跟唔上勇武</span><br />\n<br />\n呢期文宣真係少左，外國線又跟唔切<br />\n由奇依家火箭GM單野搞到美國人好關注<br />\n但關注還關注，佢地仲未識主動上網搵<br />\n希望大家幫手餵埋比佢地，貼多啲文宣解釋點解我地做緊乜。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住大家，可能我叫大家休息唔係條岩既路，我唔清楚。但好肯定既係，核爆都唔割，勇武無做錯。<br />\n<br />\n就算休息，大家唔係真係訓，係轉戰場。<br />\n<br />\n都歡迎大家屌我 歡迎討論。<br />\n<br />\n文宣好缺人，由奇外國文宣組。一齊玩twitter reddit ig fb <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4R8mnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4R8mnV.jpg&h=2a50df6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmKt5PB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmKt5PB.jpg&h=112af1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXApD9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXApD9C.jpg&h=93e20432&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426677a9bedeb18ca4c69cd9fe4f68ad29660619","tid":1634520,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"休唔休我唔知<br />\n但文宣求大家幫手"},{"pid":"d52022a4a9a2423fdae50a4cc86ffd6f46f42eec","tid":1634520,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"打左四個月，有D野你地唔肯做，就點都輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6ade6aa48eb7071bf82451c4409cc5025854c8a","tid":1634520,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"休唔休我唔知<br />\n但文宣求大家幫手"},{"pid":"7e